response.overview: An Exciting and Intriguing look at the world of HULKAMANIA! Exclusive interviews with Hulkster himself. Plus...Coliseum Video Exclusive WWF Matches! See...Hulk Hogan battle such opponents as Ted DiBiase, the Genius, Macho King Randy Savage, Earthquake, and Ultimate Warrior. Also...Never Before Seen! An earthshaking, edge of your seat exclusive Tag-Team matchup of Hulk Hogan & Tugboat vs. Earthquake & Dino Bravo! Bonus...A behind the scene exclusive look at the making of Hulk's latest major motion picture- Suburban Commando!
response.title: Hulkamania Forever
